FBIS4-42472 "drweu107_i_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 FRANCE Foreign Ministry Condemns Israeli Raid on Lebanon Foreign Ministry Condemns Israeli Raid on Lebanon LD0206150494 Paris Radio France International in French 1400 GMT 2 Jun 94 LD0206150494 Paris Radio France International French BFN [Excerpts] Tension runs high again in the Middle East after a raid by the Israeli Air Force on a base of the pro-Iranian Hizballah in the Biqa' Valley, a few kilometers from the Syrian border. [passage omitted] The French Ministry of Foreign Affairs has condemned the Israeli raid, describing it as a violation of Lebanese sovereignty.
